  "remarks": "President of the Partizanski District court of Minsk, former Deputy President of the Frunzenski District court of Minsk, former judge of the Frunzenski District of Minsk, dealing with the cases of Aleksandr Otroshchenkov (sentenced to a 4 years restricted imprisonment), Aleksandr Molchanov (3 years) and Dmitri Novik (3.5 years of restricted imprisonment). Responsible for implementing the politically-motivated administrative and criminal sanctions against representatives of civil society.",
